  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 4 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  mandatory: 0
  lines:
  - AN UPDATE ON THE VIRUS
  - We have once again been able to confirm an additional symptom of the virus.
  - Infected individuals experience irregular speech patterns, that is inconsistent
    in coherence without apparent reason.
  - This symptom alone can be indicative of being infected.
  - AN ADDITIONAL UPDATE
  - The evacuation of citizens is nearing completion.
  - By the evening of tomorrow, all citizens are expected to have been evacuated,
    and greater measures will be put into action to remove the virus and reallow
    citizens to inhabit the dome safely.
  - Thank you to all citizens for their compliance and support.
